thread.title: Trevar Mosley

author: Trevar Mosley
title: Trevar Mosley
text: Company did an excellent job of repairing my computer . They communicated very clearly and effectively when my part would be done as well as the problems that were present . They immediately notified me that they needed an additional part (which was no charge)when the part will be in, and when I could expect my part to be back to me. With that said I still received my part back a day ahead of when I was told I would receive it . Now I'm back to driving my truck and couldn't be more happy .
